highlights.text: “Sex” by Cheat Codes and Kris Kross Amsterdam is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 56 spots at #104.
“The Greatest (feat. Kendrick Lamar)” by Sia and Kendrick Lamar is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #54.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Starboy” is the highest at #1.
“Starboy” by The Weeknd and Daft Punk has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 2 weeks straight.
